title: Colin Cowherd's Blazing 5: 10/13/2018
itunes:title: Colin Cowherd's Blazing 5: 10/13/2018
description:
Coming off another winning week Colin talks with RJ Bell of Pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio about his Blazing 5 picks and RJ tells him which ones the wise guys in Vegas agree or disagree with. Plus, Colin throws in another NFL pick that was not a part of his original Blazing 5.
